title: Donald Trump filmography
added: * In the 1988 ''[[Sesame Street]]'' introduced the character Donald Grump, a scheming landlord Muppet who takes over Oscar the Grouch's trash can home and replaces it with "Grump Tower", then tries to evict Oscar from his own turf.
